originalText.text: Do not park your car here! The car attendants are very rude and disrespectful. Even the owners of the garage do not know how to talk to their customers. When they are wrong, they will yell at you to seem right. All the money I pay for monthly parking (almost $300 per month) and the workers treat you as if  you pay $5 to park. They will give your car away to people just because they say "the owner gave me permission to take the car".You are supposed to tell the attendants the code to the car when someone goes to pick it up. After such incident, I do not feel safe parking my car here, for anyone can walk to the attendants and get your car. Horrible experience at the garage. There are plenty of other garages in the area that offer better customer service and parking. I'm telling you save the headache and trouble by parking else where.

Horrible service
I stayed in the lot for less than 10 minutes and had to leave due to an emergency. The lady wanted to charge me for the full day when I wasn't even there for a half hour. When I told her I wouldn't pay for it she began to insult me, and got extremely rude. She made racist comments and told me not to come back there. Her service was absolutely offensive and I would like to report this to somebody.
